---
title: "An Analysis of Taylor Swift's Discography"
---

Let's take a look at how Taylor Swift's music has evolved over time!

```{r}
taylorswift <- read.csv("taylorswift.csv")
head(taylorswift)

library(stringr)
genres <- c('Country', 'English', 'USA', 'Country_Rock', 'American_Folk', 'Folk', 'Ballad')
genre_vectors <- str_split(genres, " ")  
print(genre_vectors)


```
